## Deployment

### GitHub Actions CI/CD

Automatic deployment on push to `main` branch.

**Required secrets:**
- `VPS_HOST` — Server IP
- `VPS_USER` — SSH username
- `VPS_SSH_KEY` — Private SSH key

### Manual Deployment

```bash
# SSH to server
ssh user@your-server.com

# Clone repo
git clone https://github.com/yourusername/{{ project_slug }}.git
cd {{ project_slug }}

# Deploy
docker-compose up -d
```

